                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28693566/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59325588/" class=" " title="alfred">alfred</a>
                (stop making sense)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28693566">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">本书写作有个特点：最重要的话都写在段尾。若只是梳理观点，我觉得通读段尾足矣。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-09-23 22:02</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                本书写作有个特点：最重要的话都写在段尾。若只是梳理观点，我觉得通读段尾足矣。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







